## Context and challenges
Peer Ladder is a peer-mentoring initiative that empowers underrepresented digital Research Technical
Professionals (dRTPs)

## Aims and Objectives
PeerLadder adapts the successful ELEAD programme ELIXIR’s mentoring and leadership development programmefor women – to the UK dRTP community.
ELIXIR Europe’s life science data infrastructure, depends not only onresearchers but also on dRTPs. ELEAD targeted a similar European cohort and demonstrated
measurable outcomes within a year

## Potential impact and benefits
Outcomes will feed into DisCouRSE, ELIXIR-UK, and SSI to shape inclusive leadership and EDI policy across the digitalresearch community.
